#description
Your home for Bankrate developer documentation. Start with **Getting Started** for access, authentication, your first request, SDKs, rate limits, errors, and webhooks. Use the **Partner Profile Ingestion** reference when you are integrating SFTP-delivered profiles and the batch offer generation API.
