## Guides library

This page is the parent for focused walkthroughs and references. **Getting Started** is the path for everyday Bankrate APIs. The **Partner Profile Ingestion & Offer Generation** document is a technical specification for partners who need CSV-based profile intake and batch offer responses. Additional portal topics may appear in the navigation as they are published.

